name: Alfamix
description:
Alfamix is great for creating book covers, album covers, intricate landscapes and rich art. It's also good for detailed portraits. You can create highly detailed images. See examples and prompts.

Note! This model for generating images in large numbers of steps, from 120 to 150 steps. Resolution 512x640, 640x512 or 512x704, 704x512 and must use Hires. fix, with upscaler ESRGAN_4x, Denoising strength 0.3-0.5, Hires steps 100-150, Upscale by 2-3.

The model can also work on small steps, but use 100-150 steps + Hires. fix for best results.

This model was created on SD 1.5 Automatic1111 WebUI using the Checkpoint Merger tool.

For best results use the VAE

Models used for merging:

-          v1-5-pruned

-          https://civitai.com/models/10720/jim-eidomode

-          https://civitai.com/models/4823/deliberate

-          https://civitai.com/models/3950/art-and-eros-aeros-a-tribute-to-beauty

-          https://civitai.com/models/10391/noise-offset-for-true-darkness-in-sd

-          https://civitai.com/models/4550/ayonimix

-          https://civitai.com/models/5952/experience

Special thanks to the authors of these wonderful models!
